data.label: LibJPEG
data.description: 此包包含用于实现 JPEG 图像编码、解码和转码的 C 软件。JPEG 是一种标准化的全彩色和灰度图像压缩方法。

data.label: LibJPEG
data.description: This package contains C software to implement JPEG image encoding, decoding, and transcoding. JPEG is a standardized compression method for full-color and grayscale images.
